Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:26.86,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3\an7\pos(838,20)\xshad-3}透過鏡子想寓目的 只有你的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.08,0:23:32.61,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3\an7\pos(838,20)\xshad-3}除此我別無它求
